                                                  Regions benefiting from coverage

                     Business Question
Which regions benefit the most from increased coverage? 
              
                       Query
           SELECT 
             region,
             ROUND(AVG(coverage),2)Avg_coverage,
             SUM(deaths_prevented) AS total_benefit
           FROM cancer_data
           GROUP BY region
            ORDER BY total_benefit DESC;

                       Insight
Regions with higher total deaths prevented are already seeing the benefits of better healthcare systems.

                  Recommendation
We need to Improve our healthcare systems in weaker regions.
